{
  "action": "pipeline",
  "pipeline_id": "sales-outbound-initial-contact",
  "version": "2.0.0",
  "name": "Sales Outbound — Initial Contact Workflow",
  "description": "アウトバウンドコール記録からインテント分類・リード評価・フォローアップメール草案・ゲートアーティファクトを生成する sales_outbound Track 用パイプライン。",
  "_migration_note": "v2: Typed Flow format (role/produces/consumes). v1 used type + export_as.",
  "context": {
    "mission_id": "",
    "project_name": "",
    "language": "ja",
    "prospect_name": "",
    "prospect_person_slug": "",
    "prospect_org": "",
    "call_date": ""
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "log_start",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": { "message": "📞 [OUTBOUND] Starting outbound contact workflow (mission: {{mission_id}}, prospect: {{prospect_org}})" }
    },
    {
      "id": "read_transcript",
      "role": "source",
      "op": "system:read_file",
      "produces": { "channel": "transcript_text", "type": "TranscriptText" },
      "params": { "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/cold-call-transcript.txt" }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_transcript",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": { "message": "📄 Cold call transcript loaded ({{mission_evidence_dir}}/cold-call-transcript.txt)" }
    },
    {
      "id": "classify_intent",
      "role": "transform",
      "op": "reasoning:analyze",
      "consumes": "transcript_text",
      "produces": { "channel": "intent_classification", "type": "IntentClassification" },
      "params": {
        "instruction": "以下のアウトバウンドコール記録を読み、顧客の反応を分析してください。\n\n## 分析項目\n1. 顧客の関心度（high/medium/low/none）\n2. 表明された課題・ペインポイント（箇条書き）\n3. 懸念点・障壁（箇条書き）\n4. 次ステップの合意内容\n5. インテント分類（appointment_set / needs_followup / not_interested / wrong_contact）\n\n## 出力形式（Markdown）\n### インテント分類\n### 関心度\n### 顧客の課題\n### 懸念点・障壁\n### 合意した次ステップ\n### 推奨アクション",
        "context": ["{{mission_id}}", "{{prospect_org}}", "{{prospect_name}}"]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_intent",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": { "message": "🎯 [OUTBOUND] Intent classified → {{mission_evidence_dir}}/intent-classification.md" }
    },
    {
      "id": "write_intent",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "code:write_artifact",
      "consumes": "intent_classification",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/intent-classification.md",
        "content": "{{intent_classification}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "qualify_lead",
      "role": "transform",
      "op": "reasoning:analyze",
      "consumes": "intent_classification",
      "produces": { "channel": "qualification_result", "type": "LeadQualification" },
      "params": {
        "instruction": "以下のコール記録とインテント分析に基づき、このリードを評価してください。\n\n## 評価基準（BANT）\n- Budget（予算）: 予算の言及はあるか？規模感は？\n- Authority（決裁権）: 話した相手は意思決定者か？\n- Need（ニーズ）: 明確な業務課題があるか？\n- Timeline（時期）: 導入時期の目安は？\n\n## 出力形式（Markdown）\n### BANT評価サマリー\n| 項目 | スコア(1-5) | 根拠 |\n|---|---|---|\n| Budget | | |\n| Authority | | |\n| Need | | |\n| Timeline | | |\n\n### 総合評価（hot/warm/cold）\n### 優先度スコア（100点満点）\n### 資格判定（qualified/unqualified/needs_more_info）\n### 推奨次アクション",
        "context": ["{{mission_id}}", "{{prospect_org}}"]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "write_qualification",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "code:write_artifact",
      "consumes": "qualification_result",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/lead-qualification.md",
        "content": "{{qualification_result}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_qualification",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": { "message": "✅ [OUTBOUND] Lead qualification written → {{mission_evidence_dir}}/lead-qualification.md" }
    },
    {
      "id": "draft_followup",
      "role": "transform",
      "op": "reasoning:analyze",
      "consumes": "qualification_result",
      "produces": { "channel": "followup_email", "type": "FollowupEmail" },
      "params": {
        "instruction": "以下のコール記録を踏まえ、アポイントメント確認メールを作成してください。\n\n## メール要件\n- 宛先: {{prospect_name}}（{{prospect_org}}）\n- 差出人: 市村基信（SBIセキュリティソリューションズ）\n- 内容: コールでの会話を踏まえたアポイント確認 / Zoom招待詳細 / 事前共有資料の案内\n- トーン: 丁寧かつビジネスライク。売り込み感を出しすぎない\n- 長さ: 300字以内（簡潔に）\n\n## 出力形式\n件名: \n本文:\n（署名ブロック省略）",
        "context": ["{{mission_id}}", "{{prospect_name}}", "{{prospect_org}}", "{{call_date}}"]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "write_followup",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "code:write_artifact",
      "consumes": "followup_email",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/followup-email-draft.md",
        "content": "{{followup_email}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_followup",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": { "message": "📧 [OUTBOUND] Follow-up email draft written → {{mission_evidence_dir}}/followup-email-draft.md" }
    },
    {
      "id": "record_qualification_gate",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:write_file",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/qualification-gate.json",
        "content": {
          "gate": "LEAD_QUALIFICATION_GATE",
          "track": "sales_outbound",
          "status": "pending_operator_confirmation",
          "prospect": "{{prospect_org}} / {{prospect_name}}",
          "artifacts": [
            "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/intent-classification.md",
            "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/lead-qualification.md",
            "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/followup-email-draft.md"
          ],
          "instructions": "リード評価結果を確認し、アポイントメント確認メールを送付したら status を 'passed' に更新してください。リードが非適格の場合は 'failed' として理由を記録してください。",
          "created_at": "{{$now}}"
        },
        "format": "json"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "create_email_draft",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "email:create_draft",
      "consumes": "followup_email",
      "params": {
        "to": "{{prospect_email}}",
        "subject": "【ご確認】{{prospect_org}} 様 — ミーティングのご案内",
        "body_file": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/followup-email-draft.md"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_email_draft",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": { "message": "✉️ [OUTBOUND] Follow-up email draft created in Mail.app → To: {{prospect_email}}" }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_done",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": { "message": "🏁 [OUTBOUND] Pipeline complete. Artifacts in {{mission_evidence_dir}}. Next: review Mail.app draft → send → confirm appointment → run discovery pipeline." }
    }
  ]
}
